A former Chairman of Punch, Chief Ajibola Ogunsola, has advised the management and staff of Daily Trust to continue to practise journalism professionally, arguing that good journalism can still thrive despite the changes being introduced by technology. He spoke at a panel discussion on “Journalism as Business-News, Views and Advertising” organised by the Daily Trust to commemorate its 20th anniversary. Ogunsola, who was the chairman of the occasion, congratulated the company for the feat.